Introduction

Nana is a Japanese singer under FNC Entertainment Japan. She is a member of the Japanese girl group PRIKIL and the South Korean project girl group UNIS.

She is best known for participating in the Japanese survival show Who Is Princess? and South Korean survival show Universe Ticket.

She represented Universe Ticket at the SBS Entertainment Awards 2023 along with 7 others on 30th December. They performed "Come With Me?" and "Smoke" (with Dynamic Duo).
